  "aiSummary": "# Universal Tuya Zigbee GitHub Activity Summary\n\n## New Device Requests\n- **Moes ZigBee Smart PIR Motion Sensor**  \n  - Fingerprint: `_TYZB01_geepvxsy`  \n  - Driver: `motion_sensor`  \n  - [Issue #814](https://github.com/JohanBendz/com.tuya.zigbee/issues/814) (Closed)\n\n## Supported Fingerprints\nThe following fingerprints are now supported with their respective drivers:\n\n1. **Climate Sensors**\n   - `_TZ2000_a476raq2` - `climate_sensor`, `lcdtemphumidsensor`\n   - `_TZ2000_xogb73am` - `climate_sensor`, `lcdtemphumidsensor`\n   - `_TZ3000_402jjyro` - `climate_sensor`, `contact_sensor`\n   - `_TZ3000_yxqnffam` - `climate_sensor`, `contact_sensor`\n   - `_TZ3000_6zvw8ham` - `bulb_rgb`, `contact_sensor`\n   - `_TZ3000_zmy1waw6` - `climate_sensor`, `switch_1gang`\n   - `_TZ3000_bjawzodf` - `climate_sensor`, `lcdtemphumidsensor`\n   - `_TZ3000_itnrsufe` - `climate_sensor`, `lcdtemphumidsensor`\n   - `_TZ3000_yd2e749y` - `climate_sensor`, `lcdtemphumidsensor`\n   - `_TZ3210_ncw88jfq` - `gas_detector`, `lcdtemphumidsensor`\n\n2. **Curtain Motors**\n   - `_TZE200_nkoabg8w` - `curtain_motor`, `curtain_motor_tilt`\n   - `_TZE200_xuzcvlku` - `curtain_motor`, `curtain_motor_tilt`\n   - `_TZE200_wmcdj3aq` - `curtain_motor`, `shutter_roller_controller`\n   - `_TZE200_hsgrhjpf` - `curtain_motor`, `curtain_motor_tilt`\n\n3. **Switches**\n   - `_TYZB01_xph99wvr` - `contact_sensor`, `switch_1gang`\n   - `_TYZB01_zsl6z0pw` - `switch_1gang`, `switch_2gang`\n   - `_TZ3000_4js9lo5d` - `switch_1gang`, `switch_2gang`\n\n4. **Gas Detectors**\n   - `_TZ3000_ywagc4rj` - `gas_detector`, `lcdtemphumidsensor`\n\n## New Fingerprints from Forks\n- No new fingerprints from forks were identified in the latest activity.\n\n## Pull Requests with Useful Changes\n1. **[PR #10](https://github.com/dlnraja/com.tuya.zigbee/pull/10)** - Update driver.compose.json (Closed, not merged)\n   - Added support for `_TZ3000_mrpevh8p`.\n\n2. **[PR #45](https://github.com/dlnraja/com.tuya.zigbee/pull/45)** - Update driver.compose.json (Closed, merged)\n   - Added support for `_TZE200_nv6nxo0c`.\n\n3. **[PR #46](https://github.com/dlnraja/com.tuya.zigbee/pull/46)** - Adding support for MOES/Tuya Zigbee AM25 Tubular Motor (Closed, not merged)\n   - Added support for `_TZE200_nv6nxo0c`.\n\n4. **[PR #1350](https://github.com/JohanBendz/com.tuya.zigbee/pull/1350)** - Added TS110E driver (Open)\n   - Supports `_TZ3210_ngqk6jia`, `_TZ3210_weaqkhab`.\n\n5. **[PR #1253](https://github.com/JohanBendz/com.tuya.zigbee/pull/1253)** - Added 3 new devices (Open)\n   - Supports `_TZE200_pay2byax`, `_TZ3000_mrpevh8p`.\n\n6. **[PR #1219](https://github.com/JohanBendz/com.tuya.zigbee/pull/1219)** - Update driver.compose.json (Open)\n   - Added support for `_TZ3000_gjrubzje`.\n\n7. **[PR #1218](https://github.com/JohanBendz/com.tuya.zigbee/pull/1218)** - Update driver.compose.json (Open)\n   - Added support for `_TZE204_dapwryy7`.\n\n8. **[PR #1195](https://github.com/JohanBendz/com.tuya.zigbee/pull/1195)** - Add `_TZE204_bjzrowv2` (Open).\n\nFor further details, please refer to the respective GitHub issues and pull requests."
